{"tid":1387753,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[新蒲崗]有麻雀館照住o既連儂牆","createTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:32.000Z","uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ff4da4a60bc7a6cb8effd12e7eecc125347555e","tid":1387753,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T15:03:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190730/s00001/1564498386819/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-emily-online%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e8%92%b2%e5%b4%97%e9%ba%bb%e5%b0%87%e9%a4%a8%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85%e8%88%877-21%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e8%a5%b2%e6%93%8a%e7%84%a1%e9%97%9c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190730%2Fs00001%2F1564498386819%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b-emily-online%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%2592%25b2%25e5%25b4%2597%25e9%25ba%25bb%25e5%25b0%2587%25e9%25a4%25a8%25e6%25be%2584%25e6%25b8%2585%25e8%2588%25877-21%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e6%2593%258a%25e7%2584%25a1%25e9%2597%259c&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=eff644c3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e6%25b8%25af%25e8%2581%259e%2Farticle%2F20190730%2Fs00001%2F1564498386819%2F%25e3%2580%2590%25e9%2580%2583%25e7%258a%25af%25e6%25a2%259d%25e4%25be%258b-emily-online%25e3%2580%2591%25e6%2596%25b0%25e8%2592%25b2%25e5%25b4%2597%25e9%25ba%25bb%25e5%25b0%2587%25e9%25a4%25a8%25e6%25be%2584%25e6%25b8%2585%25e8%2588%25877-21%25e5%2585%2583%25e6%259c%2597%25e8%25a5%25b2%25e6%2593%258a%25e7%2584%25a1%25e9%2597%259c&h=fc6437e7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%e6%b8%af%e8%81%9e/article/20190730/s00001/1564498386819/%e3%80%90%e9%80%83%e7%8a%af%e6%a2%9d%e4%be%8b-emily-online%e3%80%91%e6%96%b0%e8%92%b2%e5%b4%97%e9%ba%bb%e5%b0%87%e9%a4%a8%e6%be%84%e6%b8%85%e8%88%877-21%e5%85%83%e6%9c%97%e8%a5%b2%e6%93%8a%e7%84%a1%e9%97%9c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日網上有網民話，新蒲崗「利龍麻雀館」外嘅電子螢幕，出現澄清同元朗襲擊事件無關嘅內容。Emily係facebook見到一個前日建立、名為「利龍集團」專頁，睇到由「利龍麻雀娛樂公司」發出嘅聲明。聲明話，近日有傳7月21日元朗襲擊事件中，有3個參與者同公司有關。公司澄清話，同嗰3名白衣男子毫無關係，坊間傳言實屬誤會，亦話「我等良好公民與違法者劃清界線」。<br />\n<br />\n聲明仲話，要求政府回應五大訴求，包括正式撤回《逃犯條例》、收回暴動指控、撤銷檢控示威者、成立獨立調查委員會，還警方同示威者清白，以及盡快實施雙普選。聲明又話，風雨飄搖，「惟利龍必與港人同在」。有網民就留言「祝生意興隆」，亦有網民話「唔識打牌都想去幫襯下你哋！」<br />\n<br />\n「利龍集團」facebook之後再發文指出，喺新蒲崗錦榮街街口設置咗連儂牆，歡迎大家發表意見，但後來又話因颱風關係，連儂牆暫時拆卸，天氣轉好就會回復正常喇。佢咃亦上載相片，係「關二哥」神壇前擺咗幾支寶礦力飲品，留言話「保佑香港呀二哥」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20190730/s00001/a17d4180ce4eb49f20f994ee52e3e3d0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20190730%2Fs00001%2Fa17d4180ce4eb49f20f994ee52e3e3d0.jpg&h=e53ac717&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}